1.0.name: wordpress/category-ajax-chain-selects
1.0.description:
This plugin makes it easy to have chain select category/custom taxonomy drop downs in your theme using Ajax.

The plugin was created as a way for me to use chain selects on a number of websites I have built over the past few years. As it was my first attempt at making a Wordpress plugin, I thought it would be best to go back and update it to work with the latest version of WordPress and is now compatible with custom taxonomies.

Feel free to visit my website http://www.peterjharrison.me or contact me at me@peterjharrison.me

Have fun!
